    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064140/extras/5883f2a53bee549ae0ea4e68b4cbf213.avif?t=1728732819\" width=640 height=98 /></span><br><br><strong>&quot;Thou Shalt Not Kill&quot;</strong> is a VHS-style first-person walking simulator horror game. You play as Angel, a girl traveling through the forest who finds a VHS tape lying on the ground. She starts watching it, only to discover that the footage is unsettling and tells a mysterious story. As you watch the entire tape, you realize this is no ordinary VHS footage, and you are shocked by its revelations.<br><br>The game takes only 30 minutes to beat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064140/extras/28e01507f3e915a299624e4050ab1ccb.poster.avif?t=1728732819\" width=602 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064140/extras/28e01507f3e915a299624e4050ab1ccb.webm?t=1728732819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064140/extras/28e01507f3e915a299624e4050ab1ccb.mp4?t=1728732819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2>The game offers a tense atmosphere and heart-pounding vibes that will make you nervous while playing. It features 3D surround sound audio to immerse you in the scene fully, realistic graphics, creepy enemy design, a realistic dynamic flashlight system, and an overall spooky vibe.",
